  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you always dreamed of running your own pawn shop? Now it's possible with MyPawnShop!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387230/extras/c46c27d8c750d3c93778962f5827e670.avif?t=1747647718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387230/extras_big/c46c27d8c750d3c93778962f5827e670.avif?t=1747647718 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><br>You can buy and sell hundreds of items of many different types. Musical instruments, weapons, art objects and much more!<br><br>Become rich by negotiating with your customers when buying and selling.<br><br>Clean and repair your items to earn even more money, with different tools at your disposal (found at different vendors in the game).<br><br>Manage your store as you wish with different storage units available as well as your storage reserve to temporarily store your items to be repaired or cleaned.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387230/extras/00eb2f1cc7890f5f7f08730b6f88e35b.avif?t=1747647718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387230/extras_big/00eb2f1cc7890f5f7f08730b6f88e35b.avif?t=1747647718 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387230/extras/af2bba7d25d8f28960c242f3d946a424.avif?t=1747647718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387230/extras_big/af2bba7d25d8f28960c242f3d946a424.avif?t=1747647718 width=800 height=450 /></span><br>Early Access:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MyPawnShop is already available but development is still ongoing to offer you as much content as possible. Follow the development directly in-game (on the main menu) or on Steam to be aware of the news.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you always dreamed of running your own pawn shop? Now it's possible with MyPawnShop!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387230/extras/c46c27d8c750d3c93778962f5827e670.avif?t=1747647718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387230/extras_big/c46c27d8c750d3c93778962f5827e670.avif?t=1747647718 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><br>You can buy and sell hundreds of items of many different types. Musical instruments, weapons, art objects and much more!<br><br>Become rich by negotiating with your customers when buying and selling.<br><br>Clean and repair your items to earn even more money, with different tools at your disposal (found at different vendors in the game).<br><br>Manage your store as you wish with different storage units available as well as your storage reserve to temporarily store your items to be repaired or cleaned.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387230/extras/00eb2f1cc7890f5f7f08730b6f88e35b.avif?t=1747647718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387230/extras_big/00eb2f1cc7890f5f7f08730b6f88e35b.avif?t=1747647718 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387230/extras/af2bba7d25d8f28960c242f3d946a424.avif?t=1747647718\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3387230/extras_big/af2bba7d25d8f28960c242f3d946a424.avif?t=1747647718 width=800 height=450 /></span><br>Early Access:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MyPawnShop is already available but development is still ongoing to offer you as much content as possible. Follow the development directly in-game (on the main menu) or on Steam to be aware of the news.</p>",
